## Authentication

- Firebase Auth with Google sign-in only
- Restricted to `@uw.edu` email domain (enforced in `lib/auth.tsx` via `hd` param + email check after sign-in)
- `AuthProvider` wraps the app in root layout; `useAuth()` hook for access
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_SKIP_AUTH=true` bypasses auth with a mock user for local dev
- Future: officer vs member roles for posting/admin permissions

